en_44338_0	Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake, Commander of the Army on Friday (3) paid a courtesy call on the new Secretary to the Ministry of Defence, General S H. Shantha Kottegoda (Retd) at the Ministry of Defence and expressed his cooperation for conduct of his new office.
en_44338_1	During the cordial meeting, both of them exchanged views on matters of security concern and other related developments.
en_44338_2	Towards the end of the interaction, the visiting Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake presented a memento to the Secretary Defence and extended best wishes on his new appointment.
